data.description: Welcome home to this adorable all brick 3 bedroom home in the charming neighborhood of Hidden Estates! Enter in the front door and appreciate the vaulted ceiling and wood plank flooring throughout the oversized living room complete with a stunning brick focal point fireplace! The eat in kitchen area leads to the well appointed and updated kitchen complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a huge single basin stainless steel sink, and brushed nickel hardware and fixtures. This split floor plan has a great sized owner's suite with a trey ceiling as well as double vanities, two walk in closets, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. The other two bedrooms on the other side of the home have plantation shutters, ample closet space, and the front bedroom has delightful bay windows allowing for tons of natural light! The interior laundry room leads to the 2 car garage where you'll find a built in work bench. Outside through the sliding back glass door is a covered patio overlooking the flat and fenced in backyard (playset can convey!) to enjoy!
